            "author": {
                "@type": "Person",
                "name": "Southern Living Member"
            },
            "reviewBody": "This was wonderful! I used salt free butter and almond flour instead of white flour. Very tender and flaky. Cooked it for myself and would serve to guests any time. I'm not a fish person, was never served it as a kid. If you have someone who doesn't like fish, I promise they will love this.",
